query:
INSERT INTO users_subscriptions (
                id, user_id, price_id, created, expires, last_charge, status
            )
            VALUES (
                $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7
            )
            ON CONFLICT (id)
            DO UPDATE
                SET expires = EXCLUDED.expires,
                    last_charge = EXCLUDED.last_charge,
                    status = EXCLUDED.status
